dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Eau Claire County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2018. The are feature classes within the geodatabase, EauClaire_Hydro_2018.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are EAU_CLAIRE_HYDRO_2018_LINE and EAU_CLAIRE_HYDRO_2018_POLY.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://hub-eccounty.hub.arcgis.com/pages/open-data
